/contact/" target="_blank">联系表单</a>来提交。</p>\n<p>如您找到了 bug：Please post to the <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta/">Alpha/Beta area in the support forums</a>. If any known issues come up, you’ll be able to <a href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/report/6">find them here</a>. <strong>Developers,</strong> please test your plugins and themes, so that if there is a compatibility issue, we can figure it out before the final release.</p>\n<p>要测试中文版本，请至此下载 <a href="http://cn.wordpress.org/releases/#beta" target="_blank">.zip 或 .tar.gz 文件</a>。</p>\n<p>更改的内容可在安装后前往“关于”页面（工具栏 <img alt="" src="http://wordpress.org/wp-content/themes/twentyten/images/wordpress.png" /> → “关于”）来查看。</p>\n<p><code>readme.html</code> 等直接翻译文件尚未更新。请等待正式版本。</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"http://cn.wordpress.org/2012/11/25/wordpress-3-5-release-candidate/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"43";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"3.4.2 “自定义栏目”问题的解决方法";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"http://cn.wordpress.org/2012/09/09/3-4-2-custom-field-issues-confirmed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:80:"http://cn.wordpress.org/2012/09/09/3-4-2-custom-field-issues-co